snippet.title: Pokémon Sors - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
(Footage in video taken from an earlier build back from May)
After so many months of exhausting but fun development, I'm happy to announce, that Pokémon Sors is finally getting released!
Thank you all for the support and good wishes, you all are breathtaking!
This is the full release of Pokémon Sors, including the main story and the post game! Have a ton of fun playing this piece of work I'm so proud to finally give out to the public!
Anime art of characters and Logo made by Sane Cola, you are a legend m8!

Link to the Game: 
https://www.pokecommunity.com/showthread.php?t=433238

The game's discord server:
https://discord.gg/dpqNwfw

My social links:
https://linktr.ee/vytron

You can also support me on ko-fi if you like my content c:
https://ko-fi.com/vytron

Check out the sequel as well, Pokémon Sors 2:
https://www.pokecommunity.com/threads/pok%C3%A9mon-sors-2-the-vytroverse-part-4-wip.526108/

Song used:
https://youtu.be/IqkiifCbFBY

#Vytron #PokémonSors #Sors
